data.description: Sellers are Motivated & Have Reduced for you to remodel! Come see this Well Maintained Single Story, Casa Linda Home that is Within Walking Distance of Bishop Lynch & the Sought-after White Rock Montessori School. There is No Home Owners Association & there is plenty of room to Park an RV, Boat, or any other Toys. The 4-car Garage is 1092 Square feet, Insulated, and Features a Separate HVAC System Perfect for an Addition, Shop, or Hobby Space. The Roof is also a Hail-resistant Mueller Metal Roof. This Location is Close to White Rock Lake, Casa Linda Shopping, Dallas Arboretum, Highways, & downtown. There is a Formal Living Room with a Large Bay Window. This opens to the Dining Area and gallery Kitchen. The Large Breakfast Room has built-ins, a Half Bath, & a Laundry Room. The Family Room is Spacious & has a Cozy Fireplace. There are 3 Spacious Bedrooms that Feature a Jack n Jill Bath, & the 3rd Bath was Remodeled in 2023. The plumbing has also been upgraded. Enter the home from Oates.
